00:06:47.175 --> 00:06:49.575
Common mistakes and misconceptions.

00:06:50.175 --> 00:06:52.845
Please, please avoid
these common blunders.

00:06:53.265 --> 00:06:55.215
A classic is confusing.

00:06:55.275 --> 00:06:58.005
RBI's role with the Ministry of Finance.

00:06:58.395 --> 00:07:00.555
RBI is the monetary authority.

00:07:00.825 --> 00:07:02.625
The ministry is the fiscal one.

00:07:03.195 --> 00:07:06.104
Don't mix repo rate and reverse repo rate.

00:07:06.705 --> 00:07:08.505
Repo is RBI lending.

00:07:08.864 --> 00:07:11.114
Reverse repo is RBI Borrowing.

00:07:11.534 --> 00:07:14.055
Also understand NPA properly.

00:07:14.474 --> 00:07:17.805
A non-performing asset
isn't just any bad loan.

00:07:18.104 --> 00:07:22.664
It's a loan overdue by a
specific period, usually 90 days.

00:07:23.145 --> 00:07:27.315
Be careful about incorrectly
identifying regulatory bodies.

00:07:27.674 --> 00:07:29.640
Sebi does not regulate insurance.

00:07:30.099 --> 00:07:31.440
That's ida's job.

00:07:32.120 --> 00:07:35.420
A huge mistake is ignoring recent updates.

00:07:35.719 --> 00:07:38.090
Financial awareness is not static.

00:07:38.330 --> 00:07:40.070
Old facts get outdated.

00:07:40.400 --> 00:07:44.900
And finally, a silly but common
error is overlooking words like

00:07:44.900 --> 00:07:47.090
not or accept in questions.

00:07:47.510 --> 00:07:48.440
Read carefully.

